des:
From, Brainsprays, the team that helped a three year old go from phonics to reading at a second grade level comes "Letter Q. " 

Letter Q. reinforces the concept of phonics and allows early English readers to practice identifying words that start with "Q." to improve phonic fluency.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
